         TITLE 'IDAVBPJ1 - VBP JOURNAL WRITE MODULE                    *00001000

@MAINENT DS    0H                                                  0001 00004000
         USING *,@15                                               0001 00005000
         B     @PROLOG                                             0001 00006000
         DC    AL1(16)                                             0001 00007000

         DROP  @15                                                      00009000

./  ADD  SSI=70060506,NAME=IDAVBPP1
         TITLE 'IDAVBPP1 VBP RECORD MANAGEMENT MODULE                  *00001000
                        '                                               00002000
IDAVBPP1 CSECT ,                                                   0001 00003000
@PROLOG  DS    0H                                                  0002 00004000
        DS    0F                                                        00005000
        DC     V(IDAVBPO1)              ADDR OF IDAVBPO1                00006000
        DC     A(IDAVBPPR)              ADDR OF IDAVBPP1                00007000
        DC     V(IDAVBPC1)              ADDR OF IDAVBPC1                00008000
        DS     F                        NOT USED              @Z40WSSR  00009000
        DC     V(IDAVBPS1)              ADDR OF IDAVBPS1                00010000
        DC     AL1(8)                   LENGTH OF NAME                  00011000
        DC     C'IDAVBPP1'              MODULE NAME                     00012000
IDAVBPPR   STM  R14,R12,12(R13)          SAVE CALLERS REGS              00013000
        BALR   R12,R0                   SETUP BASE REG                  00014000
        DS     0H                                                       00015000
        USING   *,R12                                                   00016000
*   R11=BUFCDSPC;                   /* BASE DSPCT HEADER ON REG 11   */ 00017000
         L     R11,BUFCDSPC(,R1)                                   0082 00018000
*   RFY                                                            0083 00019000
*     VBPDSPCT BASED(R11);                                         0083 00020000
*   OSAVREG=ADDR(VBPHSAVE);         /* STORE MY SAVE AREA ADDR IN  0084 00021000
*                                      CALLERS SAVE AREA             */ 00022000
         LA    @10,VBPHSAVE(,R11)                                  0084 00023000
         ST    @10,OSAVREG(,R13)                                   0084 00024000
*   VBPHBUFC=R1;                    /* STORE BUFC ADDR IN DSPCT    0085 00025000
*                                      HEADER                        */ 00026000
         ST    R1,VBPHBUFC(,R11)                                   0085 00027000
*   VBPHSAVO=R13;                   /* STORE CALLERS SAVE AREA ADDR     00028000
*                                      IN MY SAVE AREA               */ 00029000
         ST    R13,VBPHSAVO(,R11)                                  0086 00030000

*/********************************************************************/ 00278000
*/*                                                                  */ 00279000
*/* ENTRY POINT:         VBPS1FRR                                    */ 00280000
*/*                                                                  */ 00281000
*/* PURPOSE:             VBP FRR ROUTINE ENTERED DUE TO              */ 00282000
*/*                      1. ERRORS IN MAIN LINE ROUTINE - IDAVBPS1,  */ 00283000
*/*                      2. ERRORS IN ASM(RELEASE LG) INVOKED BY 1., */ 00284000
*/*                      3. OR EXECUTION OF ABEND IN 1 OR 2.         */ 00285000
*/*                FAILURE IN IDAVBPS1 COULD BE WHILE                */ 00286000
*/*                1. RELEASING LOGICAL GROUP(PARMLIST WORD2 = 0)    */ 00287000
*/*                2. FREEING DSPCT MAP(PARMLIST WORD2 = 8)  @Z40WSSR*/ 00288000
*/*                3. FREEING DSPCT HEADER(PARMLIST WORD2 = 16)      */ 00289000
*/*                IF RETRY IS POSSIBLE THEN                 @VS06992*/ 00290000
*/*                       IF ABEND CODE IS 0E4 THEN          @VS06992*/ 00291000
*/*                 IN CASE OF 1 RETRY FREEING THE DSPCT MAP @Z40WSSR*/ 00292000
*/*                 IN CASE OF 2 RETRY FREEING THE DSPCT HEADER      */ 00293000
*/*                ELSE PERCOLATE.                                   */ 00294000
*/*                                                                  */ 00295000
*/* INPUT:               REG1 - ADDR OF SDWA                 @Z40WSSR*/ 00296000
*/*                      REG 14 - RETURN ADDR, REG 15 - ENTRY ADDR   */ 00297000
*/*                PARMLIST CONTENTS:                                */ 00298000
*/*                  WORD1 = DSPCT HEADER ADDR                       */ 00299000
*/*                  WORD2 = ERROR RECOVERY FLAG                     */ 00300000
*/*                  WORD3 = CODE REG OF IDAVBPS1                    */ 00301000
*/*                  WORD4 = BASE REG OF IDAVBPS1                    */ 00302000
*/*                                                                  */ 00303000
*/* OUTPUT:              REG 1 AND REG 14 RESTORED                   */ 00304000
*/*                      BASE REG, CODE REG & DSPCT HEADER ADDR OF   */ 00305000
*/*                      MAIN LINE MODULE IDAVBPS1 ARE RESTORED IN   */ 00306000
*/*                      CASE OF RETRY.                              */ 00307000
*/*                                                                  */ 00308000
*/* EXIT NORMAL:   SEE PURPOSE.                                      */ 00309000
*/*                                                                  */ 00310000
*/* EXIT ERROR:          PERCOLATE TO THE RECOVERY ROUTINE   @Z40WSSR*/ 00311000
*/*                      OF THE INVOKER OF IDAVBPS1          @Z40WSSR*/ 00312000
*/*                                                                  */ 00313000
*/********************************************************************/ 00314000
*                                                                  0148 00315000
*   RFY                                                            0148 00316000
*     VBPDSPCT BASED(RDWA1);        /* BASE DSPCT ON SDWA PARM LIST     00317000
*                                                            @Z40WSSR*/ 00318000
*   RFY                                                            0149 00319000
*    (R0,                                                          0149 00320000
*     R5,                                                          0149 00321000
*     R14) RSTD;                    /*                       @VS07809*/ 00322000
*   R13=R0;                         /* SET R13 = 200 BYTE WORK AREA     00323000
*                                      FOR SDUMP             @VS07809*/ 00324000
         LR    R13,R0                                              0150 00325000
*   RFY                                                            0151 00326000
*     R0 UNRSTD;                    /*                       @VS07809*/ 00327000

         L     @04,RDWA1(,@04)                                     0155 00345000

*   SDWATO1=SDWAFRM1+VBPHLEN;       /* MOVE ADDR OF END OF HEADER  0156 00347000
*                                      INTO SDWA ZM40069             */ 00348000
         LR    @03,@04                                             0156 00349000
         AL    @03,VBPHLEN(,@04)                                   0156 00350000
         ST    @03,SDWATO1(,R1)                                    0156 00351000
*   SDWAEBC=BITB;                   /* REQUEST EBCDIC PRINTOUT OF  0157 00352000
*                                      VARIABLE              @VS07089   00353000
*                                      LENGTH RECORDING AREA @VS07089*/ 00354000
         OI    SDWAEBC(R1),B'01000000'                             0157 00355000

*                                                                  0158 00357000
         O     @03,EOLMARK                                         0158 00358000
         ST    @03,SDWATO1(,R1)                                    0158 00359000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00360000
*   /*                                                               */ 00361000
*   /* ISSUE SDUMP TO DUMP DSPCT HEADER                      @Z40WSSR*/ 00362000
*   /*                                                               */ 00363000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00364000
*                                                                  0159 00365000
*   R2=ADDR(LISTS1);                /* PASS ID TO SDUMP              */ 00366000
         LA    R2,LISTS1                                           0159 00367000
*   CALL SDUMPRTN;                  /* GO ISSUE SDUMP                */ 00368000
*                                                                  0160 00369000
         BAL   @14,SDUMPRTN                                        0160 00370000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00371000
*   /*                                                               */ 00372000
*   /* IF MEMORY IS ADDRESSABLE FOR RETRY THEN                       */ 00373000
*   /*                                                               */ 00374000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00375000
*                                                                  0161 00376000
*   IF SDWAFMID=ZERO THEN                                          0161 00377000
         SLR   @04,@04                                             0161 00378000
         LH    @03,SDWAFMID(,R1)                                   0161 00379000
         N     @03,@CF02321                                        0161 00380000
         CR    @04,@03                                             0161 00381000
         BNE   @RF00161                                            0161 00382000
*     DO;                                                          0162 00383000
*                                                                  0162 00384000
*       /*************************************************************/ 00385000
*       /*                                                           */ 00386000
*       /* IF RETRY IS POSSIBLE THEN RETRY                           */ 00387000
*       /*                                                           */ 00388000
*       /*************************************************************/ 00389000
*                                                                  0163 00390000
*       IF SDWACLUP=NULLB THEN                                     0163 00391000
         TM    SDWACLUP(R1),B'10000000'                            0163 00392000
         BNZ   @RF00163                                            0163 00393000
*         DO;                                                      0164 00394000
*                                                                  0164 00395000
*           /*********************************************************/ 00396000
*           /*                                                       */ 00397000
*           /* IF RELEASE LG IS UNSUCCESSFUL THEN GO RETRY FREEMAIN  */ 00398000
*           /* FOR DSPCT MAP                                 @Z40WSSR*/ 00399000
*           /*                                                       */ 00400000
*           /*********************************************************/ 00401000
*                                                                  0165 00402000
*           IF RDWA21=ZERO THEN                                    0165 00403000
         L     @03,SDWAPARM(,R1)                                   0165 00404000
         CH    @04,RDWA21(,@03)                                    0165 00405000
         BNE   @RF00165                                            0165 00406000
*             DO;                                                  0166 00407000
*               R2=ADDR(FREEMAP);   /* LOAD INTO REG 2 ADDR OF     0167 00408000
*                                      ROUTINE TO FREE DSPCT       0167 00409000
*                                      EXTENSION IN IDAVBPS1 @Z40WSSR*/ 00410000
         L     R2,@CV02277                                         0167 00411000
*               RDWA21=EIGHT;       /* SET TRACE FLAG TO PREVENT   0168 00412000
*                                      RECURSIVE LOOP        @Z40WSSR*/ 00413000
         MVC   RDWA21(2,@03),@CH00058                              0168 00414000
*             END;                                                 0169 00415000
*                                                                  0169 00416000
*           /*********************************************************/ 00417000
*           /*                                                       */ 00418000
*           /* IF FREEMAIN MAP IS UNSUCCESSFUL THEN FREEMAIN DSPCT   */ 00419000
*           /* HEADER                                                */ 00420000
*           /*                                                       */ 00421000
*           /*********************************************************/ 00422000
*                                                                  0170 00423000
*           ELSE                                                   0170 00424000
*             IF RDWA21=EIGHT THEN                                 0170 00425000
         B     @RC00165                                            0170 00426000
@RF00165 L     @04,SDWAPARM(,R1)                                   0170 00427000
         CLC   RDWA21(2,@04),@CH00058                              0170 00428000
         BNE   @RF00170                                            0170 00429000
*               DO;                                                0171 00430000
*                 R2=ADDR(FREEDSPC);/* LOAD INTO REG 2 ADDR OF     0172 00431000
*                                      ROUTINE TO FREE DSPCT HEADER     00432000
*                                      IN IDAVBPS1                   */ 00433000
         L     R2,@CV02278                                         0172 00434000
*                 RDWA21=SIXTEEN;   /* SET TRACE FLAG TO PREVENT   0173 00435000
*                                      RECURSIVE LOOP                */ 00436000
         MVC   RDWA21(2,@04),@CH00053                              0173 00437000
*               END;                                               0174 00438000
*                                                                  0174 00439000
*           /*********************************************************/ 00440000
*           /*                                                       */ 00441000
*           /* ELSE SETRP TO PERCOLATE                               */ 00442000
*           /*                                                       */ 00443000
*           /*********************************************************/ 00444000
*                                                                  0175 00445000
*             ELSE                                                 0175 00446000
*               GO TO PERCOLAT;                                    0175 00447000
*                                                                  0175 00448000
*           /*********************************************************/ 00449000
*           /*                                                       */ 00450000
*           /* RETRY. RESET REGISTERS IN SDWA FOR RETRYING   @Z40WSSR*/ 00451000
*           /*                                                       */ 00452000
*           /*********************************************************/ 00453000
*                                                                  0176 00454000
*           SDWASR03=SDWAPARM;      /* SAVE RDWA ADDR                */ 00455000
@RC00165 L     @04,SDWAPARM(,R1)                                   0176 00456000
         ST    @04,SDWASR03(,R1)                                   0176 00457000
*           SDWASR11=RDWA1;         /* SAVE DSPCT HEADER ADDR        */ 00458000
         L     @03,RDWA1(,@04)                                     0177 00459000
         ST    @03,SDWASR11(,R1)                                   0177 00460000
*           SDWASR12=RDWA3;         /* SAVE CODE REG                 */ 00461000
         L     @03,RDWA3(,@04)                                     0178 00462000
         ST    @03,SDWASR12(,R1)                                   0178 00463000
*           SDWASR13=RDWA4;         /* SAVE SAVE REG                 */ 00464000
         L     @04,RDWA4(,@04)                                     0179 00465000
         ST    @04,SDWASR13(,R1)                                   0179 00466000
*           GO TO RETRI;            /* RETURN TO RTM FOR RETRYING    */ 00467000
         B     RETRI                                               0180 00468000
*         END;                                                     0181 00469000
*     END;                                                         0182 00470000
*                                                                  0182 00471000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00472000
*   /*                                                               */ 00473000
*   /* ELSE RETRY IS NOT POSSIBLE. PERCOLATE                         */ 00474000
*   /*                                                               */ 00475000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00476000
*                                                                  0183 00477000
*   GO TO PERCOLAT;                                                0183 00478000
         B     PERCOLAT                                            0183 00479000
*                                                                  0184 00480000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00481000
*   /*                                                               */ 00482000
*   /* ENTRY FOR RECOVERY FOR FRR - PERCOLATES               @Z40WSSR*/ 00483000
*   /*                                                               */ 00484000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00485000
*                                                                  0184 00486000
*FRRFRR:                                                           0184 00487000
*   ENTRY;                                                         0184 00488000

*   RFY                                                            0185 00490000
*     R14 RSTD;                     /*                       @Z40WSSR*/ 00491000
*   R5=R14;                         /* SAVE REGISTER 14              */ 00492000
         LR    R5,R14                                              0186 00493000

*                                                                  0189 00505000
*   RDWANAM=FRRNAM;                                                0189 00506000
         MVC   RDWANAM(24,R1),FRRNAM                               0189 00507000

         B     PERCOLAT                                            0191 00512000
*                                                                  0192 00513000
*/********************************************************************/ 00514000
*/* FUNCTION: CONSTRUCTS THE MESSAGE IN SDWAVRA WHICH DESCRIBES THE  */ 00515000
*/*  AREAS TO BE DUMPED.SCHEDULES SDUMP TO DUMP THE AREAS.           */ 00516000
*/*                                                                  */ 00517000
*/* INPUT R2 - ADDRESS OF INPUT PARAMETER LIST DEXCRIBED BY HEADRPRM */ 00518000
*/*       R3 - PARAMETER TO INDICATE DESIRED SDUMP                   */ 00519000
*/*                                                                  */ 00520000
*/* OUTPUT - UPDATED MESSAGE IN SDWAVRA, REGISTERS 6,8,7,9 ARE LOST. */ 00521000
*/********************************************************************/ 00522000
*                                                                  0192 00523000
*SDUMPRTN:                                                         0192 00524000
*   PROC OPTIONS(NOSAVE,NOSAVEAREA);                               0192 00525000
*                                                                  0192 00526000
SDUMPRTN DS    0H                                                  0193 00527000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00528000
*   /*                                                               */ 00529000
*   /* CLEAR THE SDWA VARIABLE LENGTH RECORDING AREA         @VS07390*/ 00530000
*   /*                                                               */ 00531000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00532000
*                                                                  0193 00533000
*   SDWAVRA=SDWAVRA&&SDWAVRA;       /*                       @VS07390*/ 00534000
         XC    SDWAVRA(108,R1),SDWAVRA(R1)                         0193 00535000
*   RESPECIFY                                                      0194 00536000
*    (R2,                                                          0194 00537000
*     R6,                                                          0194 00538000
*     R7,                                                          0194 00539000
*     R9,                                                          0194 00540000
*     R8,                                                          0194 00541000
*     R11,                                                         0194 00542000
*     R14) RSTD;                    /* REGISTER (2,3) = INPUT      0194 00543000
*                                      PARAMETERS, (6,7,8,9) - WORK     00544000
*                                      REGISTERS             @Z40WSSR*/ 00545000
*   RESPECIFY                                                      0195 00546000
*     HEADRPRM BASED(R2);           /* PASSED TO HEADER ROUTINE      */ 00547000
*   RESPECIFY                                                      0196 00548000
*     TABENTRY BASED(ADDR(TABLE)+HEADERBL);/* ADDRESSABILITY ON TABLE   00549000
*                                      ENTRY                         */ 00550000
*                                                                  0196 00551000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00552000
*   /*                                                               */ 00553000
*   /* IDENTIFY FAILING MODULE IN SDWA                               */ 00554000
*   /*                                                               */ 00555000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00556000
*                                                                  0197 00557000
*   RDWANAM=FRRNAM;                 /* BASIC NAME MASK               */ 00558000
         MVC   RDWANAM(24,R1),FRRNAM                               0197 00559000
*   RDWANAM(15:16)=HEADERID;        /* ACTUAL MODULE NAME            */ 00560000
*                                                                  0198 00561000
         MVC   RDWANAM+14(2,R1),HEADERID(R2)                       0198 00562000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00563000
*   /*                                                               */ 00564000
*   /* CONSTRUCT MESSAGE - MODULE NAME FIRST                         */ 00565000
*   /*                                                               */ 00566000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00567000
*                                                                  0199 00568000
*   COMPON=',VIO,';                 /* IDENTIFY IN BASIC MSG @YM08510*/ 00569000
         MVC   COMPON(5,R1),@CC02307                               0199 00570000
*   BASICMOD='IDAVBP';              /* START OF MODULE NAME          */ 00571000
         MVC   BASICMOD(6,R1),@CC02308                             0200 00572000
*   MODID=HEADERID;                 /* END OF MODULE NAME            */ 00573000
*                                                                  0201 00574000
         MVC   MODID(2,R1),HEADERID(R2)                            0201 00575000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00576000
*   /*                                                               */ 00577000
*   /* PUT BLOCKS IN - 'A(XXXX)= YYYYYY' - ONE FOR EACH BLOCK TO BE  */ 00578000
*   /* DUMPED                                                        */ 00579000
*   /*                                                               */ 00580000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00581000
*                                                                  0202 00582000
*   R6=ADDR(VARDATA);               /* FIRST SLOT FOR MESSAGE        */ 00583000
         LA    R6,VARDATA(,R1)                                     0202 00584000
*   RESPECIFY                                                      0203 00585000
*     CNBLOCK BASED(R6);            /* ADDRESSABILITY ON MESSAGE   0203 00586000
*                                      UNITS                         */ 00587000
*   R7=LENGTH(BASICMSG);            /* CURRENT MESSAGE LENGTH FOR  0204 00588000
*                                      SDWAURAL              @YM08510*/ 00589000
         LA    R7,21                                               0204 00590000
*   R9=ADDR(SDWAFRM1);              /* POINTER TO ADDRESS OF FIRST 0205 00591000
*                                      BLOCK TO DISPLAY              */ 00592000
         LA    R9,SDWAFRM1(,R1)                                    0205 00593000
*   RESPECIFY                                                      0206 00594000
*     FROMTO BASED(R9);             /* ADDRESSABILITY ON ENTRY       */ 00595000
*                                                                  0206 00596000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00597000
*   /*                                                               */ 00598000
*   /* CONSTRUCT MESSAGE BLOCK ENTRYS                                */ 00599000
*   /*                                                               */ 00600000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00601000
*                                                                  0207 00602000
*   DO R2=R2 BY LENGTH(HEADERBL) WHILE HEADERBLÂ¬='FF'X;            0207 00603000
         B     @DE00207                                            0207 00604000
@DL00207 DS    0H                                                  0208 00605000
*     IF XXXXFRMX(2:4)Â¬=ZERO THEN                                  0208 00606000

         BZ    @RF00208                                            0208 00608000
*       DO;                                                        0209 00609000
*         CNSTART=',A(YYYY)=';      /* START OF MESSAGE      @YM08510*/ 00610000
         MVC   CNSTART(9,R6),@CC02311                              0210 00611000
*         CNBLKID=TABENTRY;         /* BLOCK NAME                    */ 00612000
*                                                                  0211 00613000
         LA    @15,TABLE                                           0211 00614000
         SLR   @10,@10                                             0211 00615000
         IC    @10,HEADERBL(,R2)                                   0211 00616000
         ALR   @15,@10                                             0211 00617000
         MVC   CNBLKID(4,R6),TABENTRY(@15)                         0211 00618000
*         /***********************************************************/ 00619000
*         /*                                                         */ 00620000
*         /* CONSTRUCT EBCDIC ADDRESS                                */ 00621000
*         /*                                                         */ 00622000
*         /***********************************************************/ 00623000
*                                                                  0212 00624000
*         UNPK(CNADDRX,XXXXFRMX);   /* SORT OF UNPACKED DECIMAL      */ 00625000
         UNPK  CNADDRX(7,R6),XXXXFRMX(5,R9)                        0212 00626000
*         TR(CNADDR,TAB);           /* EBCDIC                        */ 00627000
         TR    CNADDR(6,R6),TAB                                    0213 00628000
*         R6=R6+LENGTH(CNBLOCK);    /* NEXT MESSAGE SLOT             */ 00629000
         LA    @15,15                                              0214 00630000
         ALR   R6,@15                                              0214 00631000
*         R7=R7+LENGTH(CNBLOCK);    /* CURRENT LENGTH OF MESSAGE     */ 00632000
         ALR   R7,@15                                              0215 00633000
*       END;                                                       0216 00634000
*     R9=R9+EIGHT;                  /* NEXT SDWAFRM - TO PAIR        */ 00635000
@RF00208 AL    R9,@CF00058                                         0217 00636000
*   END;                                                           0218 00637000
         AL    R2,@CF00065                                         0218 00638000
@DE00207 CLI   HEADERBL(R2),255                                    0218 00639000
         BNE   @DL00207                                            0218 00640000
*   SDWAURAL=R7;                    /* LENGTH OF MESSAGE             */ 00641000
         STC   R7,SDWAURAL(,R1)                                    0219 00642000
*                                                                  0220 00643000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00644000
*   /*                                                               */ 00645000
*   /* SDUMP AREAS REQUESTED IN THE SDWA ONLY IF MEMORY IS AVAILABLE */ 00646000
*   /*                                                               */ 00647000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00648000
*                                                                  0220 00649000
*   IF SDWAFMID=ZERO THEN                                          0220 00650000
*                                                                  0220 00651000
         LH    @15,SDWAFMID(,R1)                                   0220 00652000
         N     @15,@CF02321                                        0220 00653000
         LTR   @15,@15                                             0220 00654000
         BNZ   @RF00220                                            0220 00655000
*     /***************************************************************/ 00656000
*     /*                                                             */ 00657000
*     /* AND IF IT IS NOT A MACHINE CHECK THEN ONLY DO SVCDUMP       */ 00658000
*     /*                                                             */ 00659000
*     /***************************************************************/ 00660000
*                                                                  0221 00661000
*     IF SDWAMCHK=NULLB THEN                                       0221 00662000

*       DO;                                                        0222 00665000
*         R11=R1;                   /* SAVE REGISTER 1               */ 00666000
*                                                                  0223 00667000
         LR    R11,R1                                              0223 00668000
*         /***********************************************************/ 00669000
*         /*                                                         */ 00670000
*         /* FORMAT ESTAE PARAMETER LIST                             */ 00671000
*         /*                                                         */ 00672000
*         /***********************************************************/ 00673000
*                                                                  0224 00674000
*         ESTAEPRM=ESTAEPRM&&ESTAEPRM;                             0224 00675000

*         /***********************************************************/ 00680000
*         /*                                                         */ 00681000
*         /* MOVE IN JOB NAME                                @Z40WSSR*/ 00682000
*         /*                                                         */ 00683000
*         /***********************************************************/ 00684000
*                                                                  0226 00685000
*         JOBNAME=TIOCNJOB;         /* MOVE FROM TIOT        @YM08510*/ 00686000

*         /***********************************************************/ 00691000
*         /*                                                         */ 00692000
*         /* BRANCH ENTRY TO SDUMP REQUESTED - ACQUIRE AN FRR ROUTINE*/ 00693000
*         /*                                                         */ 00694000
*         /***********************************************************/ 00695000
*                                                                  0227 00696000
*         R2=ADDR(FRRFRR);                                         0227 00697000
         L     R2,@CA02296                                         0227 00698000
*         GEN REFS(R2,PSA,PSACSTK,FRRSCURR,FRRS,FRRSLAST,FRRSELEN, 0228 00699000
*             FRRSPARM,PSALSFCC) SETS(R2,R6,R7,FRRSCURR,FRRSFRRA,  0228 00700000

*         /*                                                         */ 00706000
*         /* DUMP REGION AS IDDWIFRR MAY NOT BE ABLE TO      @Z40WSSR*/ 00707000
*         /*                                                         */ 00708000
*         /***********************************************************/ 00709000
*                                                                  0229 00710000
*         R9=R14;                   /* SAVE REGISTER 14              */ 00711000
         LR    R9,R14                                              0229 00712000
*         R8=ADDR(ASCB);            /* ADDRESS OF ASCB FOR SDUMP   0230 00713000
*                                                            @Z40WSSR*/ 00714000
         L     R8,PSAAOLD                                          0230 00715000
*         GEN REFS(SDWAFRM1,SDWAVRA,R11,CVTSDMP,ASCBASID);         0231 00716000

               MF=(E,ESTAEPRM(11)),BRANCH=YES,ASID=ASCBASID(R8)         00718000

./  ADD  SSI=71720347,NAME=IDAVBPS1
         TITLE 'IDAVBPS1 VBP SCRATCH MODULE                            *00001000
                        '                                               00002000
IDAVBPS1 CSECT ,                                                   0001 00003000
@MAINENT DS    0H                                                  0001 00004000
         USING *,@15                                               0001 00005000
         B     @PROLOG                                             0001 00006000
         DC    AL1(16)                                             0001 00007000
         DC    C'IDAVBPS1  77.172'                                 0001 00008000
         DROP  @15                                                      00009000
@PROLOG  STM   @14,@12,12(@13)                                     0001 00010000
         BALR  @12,0                                               0001 00011000
@PSTART  DS    0H                                                  0001 00012000
         USING @PSTART,@12                                         0001 00013000
*   GPR11P=GPR01P;                  /* STORE DSPCT HDR ADDR IN REG 11*/ 00014000
         LR    GPR11P,GPR01P                                       0073 00015000
*   RFY                                                            0074 00016000
*     GPR01P UNRSTD;                                               0074 00017000
*   RFY                                                            0075 00018000
*     VBPDSPCT BASED(GPR11P);       /* BASE DSPCT HDR ON REG 11      */ 00019000
*   VBPHSAVO=GPR13P;                /* SAVE CALLERS SAVE AREA ADDR IN   00020000
*                                      MY SAVE AREA                  */ 00021000
         ST    GPR13P,VBPHSAVO(,GPR11P)                            0076 00022000
*   SAVER13=ADDR(VBPHSAVE);         /* STORE MY SAVE AREA ADDR IN  0077 00023000
*                                      CALLERS SAVE AREA             */ 00024000
         LA    @10,VBPHSAVE(,GPR11P)                               0077 00025000
         ST    @10,SAVER13(,GPR13P)                                0077 00026000
*   GPR13P=ADDR(VBPHSAVE);          /* LOAD REG 13 WITH MY SAVE AREA    00027000
*                                      ADDR                          */ 00028000
         LR    GPR13P,@10                                          0078 00029000
*   VBPHSTA=SCRIND;                 /* MODULE ID INDICATOR IN DSPCT     00030000
*                                      HDR                   @Z40WSSR*/ 00031000
*                                                                  0079 00032000
         MVI   VBPHSTA(GPR11P),X'10'                               0079 00033000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00034000
*   /*                                                               */ 00035000
*   /* SET FUNCTIONAL RECOVERY(FRR) ENVIRONMENT                      */ 00036000
*   /*                                                               */ 00037000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00038000
*                                                                  0080 00039000
*   RFY                                                            0080 00040000
*    (GPR02P,                                                      0080 00041000
*     GPR03P,                                                      0080 00042000
*     GPR04P) RSTD;                                                0080 00043000
*   GPR02P=ADDR(VBPS1FRR);          /* LOAD RECOVERY ROUTINE ADDR IN    00044000
*                                      REG 2                         */ 00045000
         L     GPR02P,@CV00067                                     0081 00046000
*   GEN CODE REFS(GPR02P,PSACSTK,PSA,FRRS,FRRSCURR,FRRSELEN,FRRSLAST,   00047000
*       PSALSFCC) SETS(FRRS,GPR03P,GPR04P,FRRSCURR,FRRSFRRA,FRRSENTR,   00048000
*       FRRSPARM) NOEXIT NOFLOWS;                                  0082 00049000
*                                                                  0082 00050000
  SETFRR  A,FRRAD=(2),PARMAD=(3),WRKREGS=(3,4)                          00051000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00052000
*   /*                                                               */ 00053000
*   /* UPDATE FRR COMM. AREA                                         */ 00054000
*   /*                                                               */ 00055000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00056000
*                                                                  0083 00057000
*   RFY                                                            0083 00058000
*     RDWA BASED(GPR03P);           /* BASE FRR COMM. AREA ON REG 3  */ 00059000
*   RDWAVBPH=ADDR(VBPDSPCT);        /* LOAD DSPCT HDR ADDR IN FRR  0084 00060000
*                                      COMM AREA                     */ 00061000
         ST    GPR11P,RDWAVBPH(,GPR03P)                            0084 00062000
*   VBPHFRAR=GPR03P;                /* STORE FRR COMM. AREA ADDR IN     00063000
*                                      DSPCT HDR                     */ 00064000
         ST    GPR03P,VBPHFRAR(,GPR11P)                            0085 00065000
*   RDWA21=0;                       /* CLEAR INDICATOR       @Z40WSSR*/ 00066000
         SLR   @10,@10                                             0086 00067000
         STH   @10,RDWA21(,GPR03P)                                 0086 00068000
*   RFY                                                            0087 00069000
*     GPR12P RSTD;                                                 0087 00070000
*   RDWA3=GPR12P;                   /* SAVE CODE REG IN FRR COMM.  0088 00071000
*                                      AREA                          */ 00072000
         ST    GPR12P,RDWA3(,GPR03P)                               0088 00073000
*   RFY                                                            0089 00074000
*     GPR12P UNRSTD;                                               0089 00075000
*   RDWA4=GPR13P;                   /* STORE SAVE AREA ADDR IN FRR 0090 00076000
*                                      COMM. AREA                    */ 00077000
         ST    GPR13P,RDWA4(,GPR03P)                               0090 00078000
*   RFY                                                            0091 00079000
*    (GPR02P,                                                      0091 00080000
*     GPR03P,                                                      0091 00081000
*     GPR04P) UNRSTD;                                              0091 00082000
*   RFY                                                            0092 00083000
*     RDWA BASED(VBPHFRAR);         /* BASE FRR COMM. AREA ON DSPCT     00084000
*                                      HDR                           */ 00085000
*   IF VBPHDEL=BITB THEN                                           0093 00086000
         TM    VBPHDEL(GPR11P),B'00001000'                         0093 00087000
         BO    @RT00093                                            0093 00088000
*     GOTO FREEDSPC;                /* IF TRYING TO SCRATCH A DATA 0094 00089000
*                                      SET WHERE AN ACTIVATE LOGICAL    00090000
*                                      GROUP AT RESTART TIME       0094 00091000
*                                      INDICATED THAT THE LOGICAL  0094 00092000
*                                      GROUP HAD ALREADY BEEN      0094 00093000
*                                      RELEASED THEN ONLY FREE THE 0094 00094000
*                                      DSPCT IN THIS MODULE. FOR THIS   00095000
*                                      CONDITION MODULE IDAVBPJ2 HAS    00096000
*                                      ACQUIRED A DSPCT AND HAS SET     00097000
*                                      THE DELETED FLAG VBPHDEL ON 0094 00098000
*                                                            @ZA00139*/ 00099000
*                                                                  0095 00100000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00101000
*   /*                                                               */ 00102000
*   /* RELEASE LOGICAL GROUP VIA ASM WHICH RELEASES TO THE SYSTEM ALL*/ 00103000
*   /* THE PAGES IN THE AUXILIARY STORAGE USED TO STORE THIS VIO     */ 00104000
*   /* DATASET                                                       */ 00105000
*   /*                                                               */ 00106000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00107000
*                                                                  0095 00108000
*   RFY                                                            0095 00109000
*     ACA BASED(GPR01P);            /* BASE ASM PARM LIST ON REG 1   */ 00110000
*   RFY                                                            0096 00111000
*     GPR01P RSTD;                                                 0096 00112000
*   GPR01P=ADDR(SECSAVE);           /* MAP ASM PARM LIST ON DSPCT  0097 00113000
*                                      HEADER WORK AREA      @Z40WSSR*/ 00114000
*                                                                  0097 00115000
         LA    GPR01P,SECSAVE(,GPR11P)                             0097 00116000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00117000
*   /*                                                               */ 00118000
*   /* IF THIS DATASET WAS NEVER JOURNALED THEN USE LGN TO RELEASE   */ 00119000
*   /* LOGICAL GROUP                                                 */ 00120000
*   /*                                                               */ 00121000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00122000
*                                                                  0098 00123000
*   IF VBPHJOU=NULLB THEN                                          0098 00124000
         TM    VBPHJOU(GPR11P),B'00000001'                         0098 00125000
         BNZ   @RF00098                                            0098 00126000
*     DO;                                                          0099 00127000
*       ACAFLG1=LGNFLAG;            /* SET LGN USED FLAG             */ 00128000
         MVI   ACAFLG1(GPR01P),X'00'                               0100 00129000
*       ACALGN=VBPHLGN;             /* MOVE LGN FROM DSPCT HDR TO ASM   00130000
*                                      PARM LIST                     */ 00131000
         MVC   ACALGN(8,GPR01P),VBPHLGN(GPR11P)                    0101 00132000
*     END;                                                         0102 00133000
*                                                                  0102 00134000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00135000
*   /*                                                               */ 00136000
*   /* ELSE USE S SYMBOL TO RELEASE LOGICAL GROUP                    */ 00137000
*   /*                                                               */ 00138000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00139000
*                                                                  0103 00140000
*   ELSE                                                           0103 00141000
*     DO;                                                          0103 00142000
         B     @RC00098                                            0103 00143000
@RF00098 DS    0H                                                  0104 00144000
*       ACAFLG1=SSYMFLAG;           /* SET S SYMBOL USED FLAG        */ 00145000
         MVI   ACAFLG1(GPR01P),X'08'                               0104 00146000
*       ACASYM=VBPHSYM;             /* MOVE S SYMBOL FROM DSPCT HDR     00147000
*                                      TO ASM PARM LIST              */ 00148000
         MVC   ACASYM(8,GPR01P),VBPHSYM(GPR11P)                    0105 00149000
*     END;                                                         0106 00150000
*   RFY                                                            0107 00151000
*     GPR06P RSTD;                  /*                       @YM01136*/ 00152000
@RC00098 DS    0H                                                  0108 00153000
*   GEN;                                                           0108 00154000
*                       /* SET ASID IN ASM PARM LIST        @ZA18526*/  00155000
    L   6,548           /* POINT TO PSA OLD ASCB            @ZA18526*/  00156000
    LH  6,36(0,6)       /* GET ASID                         @ZA18526*/  00157000
    STH 6,2(0,GPR01P)   /* STORE ASID INTO ASM PARM LIST    @ZA18526*/  00158000
*   GPR06P=GPR01P;                  /* SAVE REG 1            @YM01136*/ 00159000

./  ADD  SSI=40610079,NAME=IDAVBPS2
         TITLE 'IDAVBPS2  VBP ABNORMAL TERMINATION MODULE              *00001000
                       '                                                00002000
IDAVBPS2 CSECT ,                                                   0001 00003000
@MAINENT DS    0H                                                  0001 00004000
         USING *,@15                                               0001 00005000
         B     @PROLOG                                             0001 00006000
         DC    AL1(16)                                             0001 00007000
         DC    C'IDAVBPS2  74.061'                                 0001 00008000
         DROP  @15                                                      00009000
@PROLOG  STM   @14,@12,12(@13)                                     0001 00010000
         BALR  @12,0                                               0001 00011000
@PSTART  DS    0H                                                  0001 00012000
         USING @PSTART,@12                                         0001 00013000
         L     @00,@SIZDATD                                        0001 00014000
         GETMAIN R,LV=(0)                                               00015000
         LR    @10,@01                                             0001 00016000
         USING @DATD,@10                                           0001 00017000
         ST    @13,@SA00001+4                                      0001 00018000
         LM    @00,@01,20(@13)                                     0001 00019000
         ST    @10,8(,@13)                                         0001 00020000
         LR    @13,@10                                             0001 00021000
JSCBDISP EQU 188                                                        00022000
JSCBAOS1 EQU  72                                                        00023000
JSCBAOS2 EQU 192                                                        00024000
*   GPR11P=GPR01P->RMPLPTR;         /* SAVE RMPL ADDR IN REG 11    0084 00025000
*                                                            @VS07826*/ 00026000
         L     GPR11P,RMPLPTR(,GPR01P)                             0084 00027000
*   RFY                                                            0085 00028000
*     RMPL BASED(GPR11P);           /* BASE RMPL ON REG 11   @VS07826*/ 00029000
*                                                                  0085 00030000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00031000
*   /*                                                               */ 00032000
*   /* INITIALIZATION LOGIC                                          */ 00033000
*   /*                                                               */ 00034000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00035000
*                                                                  0086 00036000
*   ESTANSET=NULLB;                 /* ESTAE EXIT DOES NOT YET EXIST */ 00037000
         NI    ESTANSET,B'01111111'                                0086 00038000
*   LKRELERR=NULLB;                 /* NO FAILURE ON RELEASE LOCK YET*/ 00039000
         NI    LKRELERR,B'01111111'                                0087 00040000
*   RCODE=ZERO;                     /* ZERO RETURN CODE              */ 00041000
         SR    @15,@15                                             0088 00042000
         ST    @15,RCODE                                           0088 00043000
*   RFY                                                            0089 00044000
*     LGCB BASED(GPR06P);           /* BASE LGCB ON REG 6            */ 00045000
*   RFY                                                            0090 00046000
*     GPR01P UNRSTD;                                               0090 00047000
*   RFY                                                            0091 00048000
*     ASCB BASED(RMPLASCB);         /* BASE ASCB OF FAILING TASK ON     00049000
*                                      ITS ADDR IN PARM LIST         */ 00050000
*   RFY                                                            0092 00051000
*     GPR06P RSTD;                                                 0092 00052000
*   GPR06P=ASCBLGCB;                /* SAVE LGCB ADDR FROM ASCB OF 0093 00053000
*                                      FAILING TASK IN REG 6         */ 00054000
         L     @14,RMPLASCB(,GPR11P)                               0093 00055000
         L     GPR06P,ASCBLGCB(,@14)                               0093 00056000
*                                                                  0094 00057000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00058000
*   /*                                                               */ 00059000
*   /* SET ESTAE COMMUNICATIONS AREA                                 */ 00060000
*   /*                                                               */ 00061000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00062000
*                                                                  0094 00063000
*   COMAR1=GPR11P;                  /* SAVE RMPL ADDR                */ 00064000
         ST    GPR11P,COMAR1                                       0094 00065000
*   COMAR2=GPR06P;                  /* SAVE LGCB ADDR                */ 00066000
         ST    GPR06P,COMAR2                                       0095 00067000
*   COMAR31=ZERO;                   /* SET TRACE FLAG                */ 00068000
         STH   @15,COMAR31                                         0096 00069000
*   COMAR32=ZERO;                   /* ,,                            */ 00070000
         STH   @15,COMAR32                                         0097 00071000
*   COMAR4=GPR12P;                  /* SAVE CODE REG                 */ 00072000
         ST    GPR12P,COMAR4                                       0098 00073000
*   COMAR5=GPR10P;                  /* SAVE DATA REG                 */ 00074000
         ST    GPR10P,COMAR5                                       0099 00075000
*   COMAR6=GPR13P;                  /* SAVE SAVE REG                 */ 00076000
         ST    GPR13P,COMAR6                                       0100 00077000
*   COMAR7=RMPLASCB;                /* SAVE ASCB ADDR                */ 00078000
         ST    @14,COMAR7                                          0101 00079000
*                                                                  0102 00080000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00081000
*   /*                                                               */ 00082000
*   /* IF NOT ABNORMAL TERM OR IF VIO DATASETS ARE NOT INVOLVED THEN */ 00083000
*   /* BYPASS PROCESSING AND RETURN TO INVOKER                       */ 00084000
*   /*                                                               */ 00085000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00086000
*                                                                  0102 00087000
*   IF RMPLTYPE=NULLB|GPR06P=ZERO THEN                             0102 00088000
         TM    RMPLTYPE(GPR11P),B'10000000'                        0102 00089000
         BZ    @RT00102                                            0102 00090000
         CR    GPR06P,@15                                          0102 00091000
         BNE   @RF00102                                            0102 00092000
@RT00102 DS    0H                                                  0103 00093000
*     DO;                                                          0103 00094000
*       RETURN CODE(ZERO);          /* RETURN TO INVOKER             */ 00095000
         L     @13,4(,@13)                                         0104 00096000
         L     @00,@SIZDATD                                        0104 00097000
         LR    @01,@10                                             0104 00098000
         FREEMAIN R,LV=(0),A=(1)                                        00099000
         SR    @15,@15                                             0104 00100000
         L     @14,12(,@13)                                        0104 00101000
         LM    @00,@12,20(@13)                                     0104 00102000
         BR    @14                                                 0104 00103000
*     END;                                                         0105 00104000
*                                                                  0105 00105000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00106000
*   /*                                                               */ 00107000
*   /* SET ESTAE ENVIRONMENT                                         */ 00108000
*   /*                                                               */ 00109000

./  ADD  SSI=81800307,NAME=IDDWIAPP
         TITLE 'IDDWIAPP - EXCP INTERCEPT APPENDAGE SIMULATOR          *00001000
                        '                                               00002000
IDDWIAPP CSECT ,                                                   0001 00003000
@PROLOG  DS    0H                                                  0002 00004000
         USING *,R15                    ADDRESSABILITY FOR BRANCH TABLE 00005000
         B     WIEXCP                   WI EXCP ENTRY POINT             00006000
         B     WICLOSE                  WI CLOSE ENTRY POINT            00007000
         DS    0H                       WI JOURNAL ENTRY POINT          00008000
         L     R15,ADWIJRN              POINTER TO JOURNAL MODULE       00009000
         BR    R15                      GO TO IDDWIJRN                  00010000
         DC    C'IDDWIAPP'             MODULE ID              @YM01137  00011000
WICLOSE  L     R15,ADWICLS              POINTER TO CLOSE MODULE         00012000
         BR    R15                      GO TO IDDWICLS                  00013000
WIEXCP   EQU   *                        *                               00014000
         BALR  R8,0                     ADDRESSABILITY IDDWIEXCP        00015000
         USING *,R8                     *                               00016000
*   R9=ADDR(IDDWIFRR);              /* RECOVERY POINT                */ 00017000
         L     R9,@CV00557                                         0146 00018000
*   GEN SETS(R9,R10,R11,FRRSCURR,FRRSFRRA,FRRSPARM) REFS(R9,PSA,PSACSTK 00019000
*       ,FRRSCURR,FRRS,FRRSLAST,FRRSELEN,FRRSPARM,PSALSFCC)        0147 00020000
*       (SETFRR A,FRRAD=(R9),PARMAD=(R9),WRKREGS=(R10,R11) );/*    0147 00021000
*                                                            @YM03030*/ 00022000
         SETFRR A,FRRAD=(R9),PARMAD=(R9),WRKREGS=(R10,R11)              00023000
*   RQESRB=R9;                      /* SAVE RECOVERY PARAMETER LIST     00024000
*                                                            @YM03196*/ 00025000
         ST    R9,RQESRB(,RQEREG)                                  0148 00026000
*   RESPECIFY                                                      0149 00027000
*     EIFRRPRM BASED(RQESRB);       /*                       @YM03196*/ 00028000
*                                                                  0149 00029000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00030000
*   /*                                                               */ 00031000
*   /* SAVE IOS REGISTER FOR SUBSEQUENT RETURN IN THE RQE            */ 00032000
*   /*                                                               */ 00033000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00034000
*                                                                  0150 00035000
*   RQENRQE=SAVERG;                 /* SAVE AREA PASSED              */ 00036000
         ST    SAVERG,RQENRQE(,RQEREG)                             0150 00037000
*   EIRQEPTR=RQEREG;                /* SAVE RQE POINTER              */ 00038000
         L     @15,RQESRB(,RQEREG)                                 0151 00039000
         ST    RQEREG,EIRQEPTR(,@15)                               0151 00040000
*   EIREG14=R14;                    /* SAVE RETURN VECTOR            */ 00041000
         ST    R14,EIREG14(,@15)                                   0152 00042000
*   EIREG5=R5;                      /* SAVE IOS BASE REGISTER        */ 00043000
         ST    R5,EIREG5(,@15)                                     0153 00044000
*   RESPECIFY                                                      0154 00045000
*    (R5,                                                          0154 00046000
*     R14,                                                         0154 00047000
*     R9,                                                          0154 00048000
*     R10,                                                         0154 00049000
*     R11) UNRSTD;                  /* RELEASE REGISTERS             */ 00050000
*                                                                  0155 00051000
*/********************************************************************/ 00052000
*/*                                                                  */ 00053000
*/* FUNCTION - SETS UP REGISTERS AND ADDRESSABILITY FOR MODULE       */ 00054000
*/*                                                                  */ 00055000
*/********************************************************************/ 00056000
*                                                                  0155 00057000
*   RESPECIFY                                                      0155 00058000
*     VDSCB BASED(VDSCBREG);        /* VDSCB AND UCB ADDRESSABILITY  */ 00059000
*   RESPECIFY                                                      0156 00060000
*     IOBSTDRD BASED(IOBREG);       /* IOB ADDRESSABILITY            */ 00061000
*   RESPECIFY                                                      0157 00062000
*     DEBBASIC BASED(RQEDEB);       /* DEB ADDRESSABILITY            */ 00063000
*                                                                  0157 00064000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00065000
*   /*                                                               */ 00066000
*   /* WICB AND WICSEEKA(APPENDAGES) ADDRESSABILITY                  */ 00067000
*   /*                                                               */ 00068000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00069000
*                                                                  0158 00070000
*   WICBREG=VDSWICB;                                               0158 00071000
         L     WICBREG,VDSWICB(,VDSCBREG)                          0158 00072000
*   RESPECIFY                                                      0159 00073000
*     WICB BASED(WICBREG);                                         0159 00074000
*                                                                  0160 00075000
*/********************************************************************/ 00076000
*/*                                                                  */ 00077000
*/* FUNCTION - INSURES THAT THE WINDOW, WICB AND VBPPL EXIST FOR THE */ 00078000
*/*      EXIST FOR THE APPENDAGE INTERCEPT AND THE TRACK MANAGER.    */ 00079000
*/*      IF THE KEY OF THE USER HAS CHANGED IT FREES THE CURRENT     */ 00080000
*/*      WINDOW AND WICB AND REACQUIRES THEM IN THE NEW USER KEY.    */ 00081000
*/*      ALSO FREE WICB AND WINDOW IF PREVIOUSLY ACQUIRED BUT A      */ 00082000
*/*      SUCCESSFUL VOPEN WAS NEVER COMPLETED AS EVIDENCED BY A      */ 00083000
*/*      NON ZERO WICB POINTER AND A ZERO DSPCT POINTER.     @ZA00121*/ 00084000
*/*                                                                  */ 00085000
*/********************************************************************/ 00086000
*                                                                  0160 00087000
*   IF((WICBREGÂ¬=0)&(VDSDSPCT=0))|(((WICPRT&'F0'X)Â¬=/*       @ZA27906*/ 00088000
*       (RQEPRT&'F0'X))&(WICBREGÂ¬=0)) THEN                         0160 00089000
         SLR   @12,@12                                             0160 00090000
         CR    WICBREG,@12                                         0160 00091000
         BE    @GL00001                                            0160 00092000
         C     @12,VDSDSPCT(,VDSCBREG)                             0160 00093000
         BE    @RT00160                                            0160 00094000
@GL00001 LA    @12,240                                             0160 00095000
         SLR   @09,@09                                             0160 00096000
         IC    @09,WICPRT(,WICBREG)                                0160 00097000
         NR    @09,@12                                             0160 00098000
         SLR   @05,@05                                             0160 00099000
         IC    @05,RQEPRT(,RQEREG)                                 0160 00100000
         NR    @12,@05                                             0160 00101000
         CR    @09,@12                                             0160 00102000
         BE    @RF00160                                            0160 00103000
         LTR   WICBREG,WICBREG                                     0160 00104000
         BZ    @RF00160                                            0160 00105000
@RT00160 DS    0H                                                  0161 00106000
*     DO;                           /*                       @ZA27906   00107000
*                                      KEY OF USER HAS CHANGED - OR     00108000
*                                      UNSUCESSFUL VOPEN FREE WICB 0161 00109000
*                                      AND WINDOW SO THEY CAN BE   0161 00110000
*                                      ACQUIRED IN THE NEW KEY.    0161 00111000
*                                                            @ZA00121*/ 00112000
*       RESPECIFY                                                  0162 00113000
*        (R9,                                                      0162 00114000
*         R10) RSTD;                /* SAVE THE RQE AND VDSCB      0162 00115000
*                                      POINTERS                      */ 00116000
*       R9=VDSCBREG;                /* VDSCB ADDRESSABILITY          */ 00117000
         LR    R9,VDSCBREG                                         0163 00118000
*       RESPECIFY                                                  0164 00119000
*         VDSCB BASED(R9);                                         0164 00120000
*       RESPECIFY                                                  0165 00121000
*         UCBOB BASED(R9);          /* UCB ADDRESSABILITY            */ 00122000
*       R10=RQEREG;                 /* RQE ADDRESSABILITY            */ 00123000
         LR    R10,RQEREG                                          0166 00124000
*       RESPECIFY                                                  0167 00125000
*         RQE BASED(R10);                                          0167 00126000
*                                                                  0167 00127000
*       /*************************************************************/ 00128000
*       /*                                                           */ 00129000
*       /* PURGE THE WINDOW - CALL THE TRACK MANAGER TO VWRITE THE   */ 00130000
*       /* WINDOW SO IT CAN BE FREED                                 */ 00131000
*       /*                                                           */ 00132000
*       /*************************************************************/ 00133000
*                                                                  0168 00134000

*                                      POINTER AT ENTRY              */ 00014000
*   R2=R13;                         /* SAVE SAVE AREA POINTER        */ 00015000
